<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>705</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>yī qiān dài guò qù 迦南705</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yī qiān dài guò qù, yī wàn dài guò qù, zhǔ de cí ài méi yǒu gǎi biàn.
 tiān zhī guǎng dà, de zhī wú biān, tiān shàng de xià yī qiè shén dōu zài zhǎng guǎn.
 wǒ men dé le shén de dà ēn diǎn, shuō bù wán de gǎn xiè a, cún zài xīn jiān.
 chàng zuì měi de shī piān, xiàn zài zhǔ miàn qián. ā bà ā bà, wǒ men xiàng nǐ yǎng jiǎn.</lyrics>
</song>